<td align="center"><b>
<i>Megachile lapponica</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Thomson, 1872</font></b><br>
<small><i>Megachile nivalis </i>Friese, 1903; <i>Megachile melanopyga amaguella </i>Cockerell, 1924; <i>Megachile lapponica baicalica_homonym </i>Cockerell, 1928; <i>Megachile lapponica var kurbati </i>Cockerell, 1928; <i>Megachile lapponica fuscifrons </i>Cockerell, 1930, replacement name; <i>Megachile &#40;Anthemois&#41; santiamensis </i>Mitchell, 1934; <i>Megachile &#40;Megachile&#41; nivalis </i>Friese, 1903; <i>Megachile &#40;Megachile&#41; lapponica ishikawai </i>Hirashima and Maeta, 1974, valid subspecies</small><p>
